{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act16side", "eventName": "吾導先路", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "GA-4", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "安魂教堂", "storyInfo": "薩科塔能夠感受彼此的情緒，而菲亞梅塔是當年的四人小隊中唯一的黎博利。莫斯提馬與蕾繆安又是否能明白菲亞梅塔的憤怒？\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g6_laterano_chapelin", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再多和我講些！", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#6$1"}, {"id": 10, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呀，小心手上的蠟燭，別燙著！", "name": "羅塞菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊！不能捏壞形狀......不然就不好看了。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了媽媽......我要做得完美一點。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好啦，我講得已經夠多的了。無非是無聊的冒險，尋常的生活。至於傳說中的卡茲戴爾......", "name": "羅塞菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說來慚愧，我們都沒有去過。", "name": "羅塞菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲的卡茲戴爾......一定就像薩科塔的拉特蘭一樣吧！是薩卡茲們的家鄉......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每個人都開開心心的，也會有棉花糖車吧？還有點心店......大街上會有好多高高興興的薩卡茲，大家互相打招呼！", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#6$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......也許是吧。", "name": "羅塞菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "終有一天。", "name": "羅塞菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該說說你了，塞茜莉亞。你的爸爸媽媽是什麼樣的人？", "name": "羅塞菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......其實，我也不太清楚......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我見到爸爸的次數很少......每次要見爸爸的時候，媽媽就會準備很久，帶著我在晚上出門，走很遠很遠......走到樹林裡。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#11$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們在森林裡見面，爸爸總是穿著厚厚的斗篷，似乎剛從遙遠的地方趕過來......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#11$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#11$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我其實不太記得爸爸的長相，但我記得爸爸的角！漆黑又筆直，在月亮下閃閃發光。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#11$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#11$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他會牽著我的手在樹林的邊緣散步，告訴我每一棵樹的種類和年齡......城外的晚上好安靜，連羽獸的叫聲都沒有，但我一點也不怕。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#11$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#11$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爸爸老是緊緊牽著我的手，其實會有一點點疼......但我不想告訴他。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#11$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每次見到爸爸，我覺得爸爸比我還要高興......！好像也有點......緊張？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我走累了，媽媽就會背著我回家。我回頭，就會看到爸爸站在高高的樹下面，一直看著我們，走了很遠很遠，他還站在那裡......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的爸爸媽媽都是了不起的人。", "name": "羅塞菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我覺得媽媽可厲害了！她什麼都會！", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#6$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，你看，這是媽媽的守護銃，艾澤爾哥哥放在我這裡了。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "媽媽說，爸爸根本打不過她......她都是讓著爸爸呢！不過我想爸爸也應該很厲害，嗯！", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈塞茜莉亞，我說的“了不起”和你說的“厲害”，可能不是同一回事。", "name": "羅塞菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎？那爸爸媽媽一定又了不起又厲害！", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#6$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，媽媽從來不和我講她和爸爸認識的故事，我每次想問，稀裡糊塗地就被媽媽繞去說別的了......為什麼媽媽不告訴我呢？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......當我們還小的時候啊，更重要的事情還有很多。你喜歡看泡茶嗎，我小時候可喜歡看泡茶啦，茶水的顏色一層一層地變化......", "name": "羅塞菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#2$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......羅塞菈姐姐，你現在繞開話題的樣子，和媽媽就很像哦......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......其實我也不是什麼都不知道。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#2$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "昨天我在城裡跑了好多地方，除了你，一個薩卡茲都沒見到......薩卡茲，不能來拉特蘭，是不是？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以爸爸和媽媽也不應該在一起......不對，我是想說，是不是有人不讓爸爸媽媽在一起？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，沒有什麼不應該在一起......這些一定會改變的。不會很久......總有一天。", "name": "羅塞菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相愛沒有罪過。", "name": "羅塞菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是嗎。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#2$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們就是為此來到這裡的。", "name": "羅塞菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到了那一天，我也可以在拉特蘭的大街上隨便亂逛了？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#5$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。", "name": "羅塞菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再也不用偷偷藏在房間裡？那拉特蘭每一家糖果店我都可以去一次嗎？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一次哪裡夠呀，塞茜莉亞喜歡去多少次就去多少次。", "name": "羅塞菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚......真希望那一天快點來......好想快點長大！", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，如果你快快長大，也許......", "name": "羅塞菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，塞茜莉亞，我們不用那麼著急。我小時候，總覺得等長大了，什麼煩惱都可以解決掉。可是，等到真的長大了......", "name": "羅塞菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長大是一件非常非常非常辛苦的事，塞茜莉亞，對你來說更是這樣，你肩負著......不，算了。你還小，別去想這些。", "name": "羅塞菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可每個人都會長大呀？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是啊，我們沒有選擇。", "name": "羅塞菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$storyendjp_intro", "key": "$storyendjp_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一直微笑著的羅塞菈露出了有些落寞的神情。"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她看向小教堂的窗外，外面是開滿鮮花的墓園，再遠處，隱約可見高踞於拉特蘭城中心的聖像。"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她輕輕哼起了歌。憂傷，又依稀帶著希望。"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，是這首歌！昨天碰到羅塞菈姐姐的時候......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#5$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "媽媽教我這首歌的時候說，歌詞她記不清楚了，就用啦啦啦代替了。可是曲調真的好好聽......本來的歌詞，是講什麼的呢？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是薩卡茲的歌，歌詞講的是一個英雄，他要出發去做了不起的事情啦，人們就唱歌和他告別，送他啟程，願他平安歸來。", "name": "羅塞菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歌裡面唱啊，英雄就要出發啦，沿著通往遠方的路，去實現他的夢想......", "name": "羅塞菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許路途遙遠，但一定，一定......", "name": "羅塞菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾澤爾哥哥，修士先生！", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#6$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在聊什麼呢？", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#8$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先導，日安——都是些有的沒的，薩卡茲以前的故事啦，再說說家常話......", "name": "羅塞菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可有意思了......我從來沒和人聊過這麼多。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾澤爾哥哥，這是你摘的花嗎？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，我想，也許可以萃取一下，給蠟燭加上香味......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#8$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "香氣可以指引離去之人的方向。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太好了，謝謝艾澤爾哥哥！", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#10$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......艾澤爾哥哥，其實......我其實......有點害怕。", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葬禮......和媽媽道別......就是真的最後一次道別了，對嗎？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的再也不能見了？就算過節也不行嗎？或者......和爸爸一樣，很久見一次......是不是也不行？就算......只是摸摸頭也不行......？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#12$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算......就算......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#9$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "媽媽......還有一個天使和馱獸的故事，沒有講完......", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#7$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塞茜莉亞......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是最後一晚了，塞茜莉亞。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塞茜莉亞，今天晚上，我陪你待在媽媽的房間吧，我們都會陪你。你們不會孤獨。", "name": "羅塞菈"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_363_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......薩卡茲為一對薩科塔母女守夜。", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "燭火雖弱，亦能照亮彼岸。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#2$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g7_laterano_ward", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$dignified_intro", "key": "$dignified_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_213_mostma_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安，我們又來看你了。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#10$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "給你帶了點甜點。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_213_mostma_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從大教堂拿出來的水果塔。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#5$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_353_1#10$2"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歡迎。順便一提，上面的仙人掌看起來很難吃。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_353_1#10$2"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_213_mostma_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不愧是你，蕾繆安，眼神真好。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#4$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_353_1#10$2"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說起來，你們有這麼想我，到了要每天來看我一次的程度？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_353_1#10$2"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_213_mostma_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要是需要，我們每個小時來看你也可以啊。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#5$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_353_1#10$2"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫斯提馬，你在獻殷勤嗎？至於菲亞梅塔......笑得很勉強哦？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_353_1#10$2"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_353_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "出事了嗎？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_353_1#1$2"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......安多恩。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_353_1#8$2"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_353_1#8$2"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_353_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你遇到他了。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_353_1#6$2"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉特蘭混進了薩卡茲，而我在追捕薩卡茲的時候......正面撞上了他的源石技藝。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_353_1#9$2"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎，沒受傷就好。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_353_1#9$2"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安，你在這裡沒問題嗎？畢竟只是普通醫院，萬一......", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#4$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_353_1#8$2"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他已經來過了。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_353_1#8$2"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說什——", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#3$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_213_mostma_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......唉。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#6$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "病房中一時寂靜。"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安看向桌上的瓶花。"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們說起他的態度，簡直就像在談論周末的野餐。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安，我不想和你生氣......", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但唯獨在這件事上......無論是你，還是莫斯提馬，每一次，每一次，我提起那時的事情，你們就會露出一樣的表情......", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看到你們的樣子，我會覺得......好像那天發瘋的人不是他，而是我。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#4$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_213_mostma_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我們只是感受到了。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#6$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又是你們薩科塔那一套？好，你感受到了，那你又為什麼向他舉銃？", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_213_mostma_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩回事。不論他當時有多......我也不可能讓他奪走鎖與匙。", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#8$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那之後呢？他害得你墮天了......！你就這樣無所謂？", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安，他的源石技藝，把你傷成這樣，在病床上昏迷了五年......你也無所謂嗎？", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_353_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "菲亞梅塔......", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_353_1#1$2"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_353_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相信我，我們是與你一邊的。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_353_1#1$2"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_353_1#9$2"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，我確實能感受......", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_353_1#9$2"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我不想再聽到這個詞。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#6$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們是不是覺得，我的生氣很多餘？", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_353_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼會呢，菲亞梅塔，我明白......", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_353_1#6$2"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對的，當然了，你們都明白。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有我不明白。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#8$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_213_mostma_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，菲亞梅塔！", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#4$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_353_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉......", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_353_1#6$2"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g11_laterano_alley", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "菲亞梅塔，菲亞梅塔！", "name": "莫斯提馬"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "微光守夜人！", "name": "莫斯提馬"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 50.0, "vibrato": 50.0, "randomness": 50.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "揍你啊！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_213_mostma_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你聽我說！", "name": "莫斯提馬"}, "figure_art": "avg_213_mostma_1#6$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫斯提馬，我告訴你！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "26_i05", "xScale": 1.0, "yScale": 1.0, "x": 150.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleTo": 0.8, "yScaleTo": 0.8, "duration": 40.0, "xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽好了，我再也受不了你們這些混蛋薩科塔了！什麼共感，什麼互相理解！我根本就不想懂！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "光環是把你們這些天使的腦子燒壞了嗎？你和蕾繆安，差點死在那片廢墟裡！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們為什麼不生氣？你們為什麼不憤怒？為什麼只有我......我的憤怒格格不入？", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別再給我擺那種故作高深的笑臉，說起什麼都無所謂的態度！你不得不離開拉特蘭，到處奔波，風餐露宿，居無定所，是拜誰所賜？！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一路跟著你到維多利亞，到萊塔尼亞，到薩爾貢，到炎國......", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你以為到底是為了什麼？！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你，蕾繆安，安多恩......我們的小隊。我們有過那麼......相互信任的時候。", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他有什麼了不得的苦衷？他憑什麼背叛這些信任？你們憑什麼要理解他？我又為什麼要理解他！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道我有多捨不得那段日子......？每一次有驚無險地完成任務......每一次蕾繆安帶我們去喝酒......每一次我們去試新開的甜品店......", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "甚至每一次他幫大家改報告......", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他有什麼理由，就隨手毀了這一切......？！！", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那樣的日子......", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那樣的日子，我是在乎的啊......", "name": "菲亞梅塔"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Image", "attributes": 